briefdescription.para: Cereal does not support the serialization of raw pointer.

detaileddescription.para: This macro enable developers to serialize a raw pointer by using the above PointerWrapper class which replace the raw pointer by a smart pointer internally.
Omar Shrit Implementation of a pointer wrapper to enable the serialization of raw pointers in cereal
